snippet.title: Survive the Nights - Official Alpha 1.0 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the trailer for Survive the Nights alpha version 1.0, the first public alpha build. We have made a lot of progress over the last two years during unlisted pre-alpha. Please check in on our development via the changelog or our Steam newsfeed.

Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/541300/Survive_the_Nights/
Discord: https://discord.gg/survivethenights
Steam News Feed: https://steamcommunity.com/app/541300/allnews/
Changelog: https://changelog.survivethenights.net/
Forum: https://community.survivethenights.net
Twitter: https://twitter.com/STNgame
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/STNgame
Website: https://www.survivethenights.net
